<div class="warranty-page">
  <h1 class="heading-1 warranty-page__title">Lifetime Warranty</h1>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Our Promise</h2>
  <p>Every piece from The Clear Cut comes with a lifetime manufacturer warranty. We stand behind the quality of our craftsmanship and materials, and we guarantee that our moissanite stones will maintain their optical properties for life.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">What's Covered</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Defects in materials and craftsmanship</li>
    <li>Moissanite stone clouding, fading, or loss of brilliance (guaranteed never to happen)</li>
    <li>Manufacturing defects in the clasp, setting, or chain</li>
    <li>Gold plating defects within the first 12 months under normal wear conditions</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="heading-3">What's Not Covered</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Normal wear and tear</li>
    <li>Damage caused by misuse, accident, or neglect</li>
    <li>Damage caused by exposure to chemicals, chlorine, or salt water</li>
    <li>Unauthorised repairs or modifications</li>
    <li>Natural gold plating wear over extended use (replating service available)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Certificate of Authenticity</h2>
  <p>Every piece comes with a Certificate of Authenticity confirming the quality and specifications of your moissanite stones. Keep this certificate with your jewelry box for warranty claims.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Making a Warranty Claim</h2>
  <p>To make a warranty claim, email <a href="mailto:hello@theclearcut.com.au" style="text-decoration:underline;">hello@theclearcut.com.au</a> with your order number, photos of the issue, and your Certificate of Authenticity. We will assess your claim and arrange a repair or replacement at no cost.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Replating Service</h2>
  <p>Over time, gold plating naturally wears with regular use. We offer a professional replating service to restore your piece to its original lustre. Contact us for pricing and turnaround times.</p>
</div>

